media:group.media:title: ITT 2019 - Martin Beeby - A Developer Primer on Blockchain
media:group.media:description: Come find out how developers can use Blockchain to build software. Understand through code how to create “smart contracts” and "chain code" and develop a different type of application that establishes trust, accountability and transparency, while streamlining business processes.
